WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.543 --> 00:00:02.691
Good morning, family!

00:00:02.691 --> 00:00:04.457
How are you all doing today?

00:00:04.766 --> 00:00:06.942
Praise the Lord, I'm excited to be here.

00:00:06.942 --> 00:00:09.880
We have some work to do in the spirit realm.

00:00:10.935 --> 00:00:19.356
I was praying about my video, and I felt the Lord correct me regarding my video about Elon Musk.

00:00:19.764 --> 00:00:29.085
The Lord, after I made that video, I had that itchy feeling and knew the Holy Spirit wasn't pleased completely with it.

00:00:29.085 --> 00:00:40.429
He said, "Brandon, I revealed this stuff to you and told you about his technology that will be used in the Tribulation.

00:00:40.819 --> 00:00:43.160
" I said, "Yes, sir, you did.

00:00:48.226 --> 00:00:58.719
" I saw the demonic spirit that was influencing his mind to help him because he has a genius IQ.

00:01:00.229 --> 00:01:10.740
When you see all that in the spirit, you start linking him with the Antichrist and making him into a bad person, saying he's going to create all this stuff.

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:24.027
It has to be created; prophecy will be fulfilled because it is prophecy from the Lord telling us what's coming in the future, and somebody had to fill that position.

00:01:24.027 --> 00:01:31.529
He's not the Antichrist, ladies and gentlemen; he is the creator of the Beast system.

00:01:31.529 --> 00:01:38.497
It does not mean that Elon Musk will implement the system; he's just creating it.

00:01:38.497 --> 00:01:44.386
So the Lord said to me, "Brandon, you've got to think bigger.

00:01:44.653 --> 00:01:47.190
" I asked, "What do you want, Lord?

00:01:47.190 --> 00:01:48.530
What are you asking?

00:01:48.865 --> 00:01:58.542
" He said to me, "Believe that Starlink, the internet system, will be used for good instead of for bad.

00:02:02.153 --> 00:02:15.620
" He said that technology can be used to spread the Gospel throughout the whole world where they don't have internet access.

00:02:15.620 --> 00:02:22.057
He said there are ways to use this as a tool for the Gospel.

00:02:22.057 --> 00:02:34.696
He said the man is blessed and told me to pray that he would get born again and help the Kingdom of God.

00:02:34.696 --> 00:02:44.986
He said, "You painted him out to be an enemy when he's already trying to help the Republican party, bringing in free speech, and doing what he did.

00:02:44.986 --> 00:02:57.217
" He said there's already a door open and told me to push it wide open and believe God for his soul.

00:02:57.217 --> 00:03:00.920
Let's call him saved today, ladies and gentlemen.

00:03:00.920 --> 00:03:06.910
Let's pray that he has a radical visitation from the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:03:07.460 --> 00:03:22.440
His technology will be used, I believe, but wouldn't it be amazing if Elon Musk got radically born again and started preaching the Gospel like another Billy Graham throughout the whole world?

00:03:22.440 --> 00:03:34.125
He is an evangelist; he has a charisma about him that draws people to him and his social media.

00:03:34.748 --> 00:03:41.371
Just think of what he could do for the Kingdom of God if we started praying for him to get radically saved.

00:03:41.371 --> 00:03:53.554
He's around Trump, and I believe with all my heart Trump is going to have a radical visitation from the Lord Jesus Christ and get baptized in the Holy Ghost in these next four years.

00:03:57.205 --> 00:04:01.050
President Trump can influence him to help him get born again.

00:04:01.050 --> 00:04:09.209
There are so many avenues here, so I want to repent even to you all for some of the things I said.

00:04:10.533 --> 00:04:15.834
You see in part and hear in part as I am growing in my own gifting.

00:04:21.109 --> 00:04:31.680
Several days later, the Lord said to me, "Brandon, you're missing it; I want you to believe me for bigger.

00:04:31.982 --> 00:04:44.520
" So I have to tell you, ladies and gentlemen, let's turn that around.

00:04:49.970 --> 00:04:50.160
I'm not attacking the man anymore.

00:04:56.693 --> 00:05:05.720
The Lord said, "You don't know where he's at with me; you don't know his soul.

00:05:12.909 --> 00:05:27.920
You judged him because of what you saw in the spirit when I was trying to show you something.

00:05:29.947 --> 00:05:43.497
I showed you part of something, but it doesn't mean you have the whole picture.

00:05:43.497 --> 00:05:57.574
" Again, it's immaturity on my part, and I want to say this: let's intercede for the man and his family.

00:05:57.574 --> 00:06:17.639
It grieved me; I passed judgment in my heart saying he's damned to hell because he's creating the Beast system, and the Lord said, "You don't know that.

00:06:17.639 --> 00:06:19.170
Who are you to say that?

00:06:19.170 --> 00:06:37.460
" When the Holy Spirit corrects you, it really makes you feel a certain way.

00:06:37.460 --> 00:06:56.306
I told all these 160,000 people who watched that video, and they're all saying they knew he was bad.

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:24.266
I get it; when you see the Beast system, you relate evil with that and think you can't pray for him.

00:07:24.266 --> 00:07:43.910
When the Lord said to me, "Call him saved, believe for his soul," I said, "God help me.

00:07:43.910 --> 00:08:12.360
" That's my heart today: to turn this ship for that man and for his family, that they would have a radical visitation from the Lord Jesus Christ and a real conversion.

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:17.520
We're still believing for the House.

00:08:22.103 --> 00:08:48.160
We see what the enemy is trying to do, folks, but greater is He that is in us than he that is in the world.

00:08:48.160 --> 00:09:16.120
We're going to take authority over the House again today and believe God for a supernatural visitation over America.

00:09:25.124 --> 00:09:45.640
I was going to go a whole different direction today about the economy and what the Lord is telling me to pray for over the next 70-some days.

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:58.737
I saw some of the enemy's tactics regarding the dollar, Putin, and Xi Jinping.

00:09:58.737 --> 00:10:08.440
There's a lot of work to be done.

00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:24.166
I made a mistake, so let's pray for him to get radically born again.

00:10:38.945 --> 00:10:45.080
Believe with all your heart because he could be a major tool for the Kingdom of the Lord.

00:10:56.299 --> 00:10:58.948
What the devil meant for bad, God can turn for good today.

00:10:58.948 --> 00:11:08.500
Wouldn't it be amazing if Starlink were a tool for the Gospel?

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:26.569
The devil might try to use it later, but we could use it now for the glory of God.

00:11:27.789 --> 00:11:40.310
The Lord said, "You've got to believe bigger; you think too small.

00:11:40.310 --> 00:11:43.720
" Elon Musk saved!

00:11:43.720 --> 00:11:47.760
I can see it.

00:11:47.760 --> 00:12:11.149
Elon Musk born again, radically baptized in the Holy Ghost, praying in other tongues, laying hands on the sick, and seeing them recover.

00:12:11.149 --> 00:12:29.515
Proclaiming Jesus Christ as Lord and having a company as a tithe machine to Jesus to help fund churches.

00:12:32.182 --> 00:12:32.537
It could happen.

00:12:34.631 --> 00:12:53.919
I prayed for Kanye West for years, and though he's having a hard time now, I'm still praying for him.

00:13:00.734 --> 00:13:13.079
I prayed for years for radical conversions for Kim Kardashian and all of them because they influence the world; why not influence the world for Jesus?

00:13:13.079 --> 00:13:21.119
God uses celebrities like Justin Bieber to bring in the harvest.

00:13:21.119 --> 00:13:26.189
It's time for Hollywood and influencers to come to Jesus.

00:13:26.199 --> 00:13:37.503
Wouldn't it be amazing if Taylor Swift got radically saved?

00:13:37.503 --> 00:14:17.959
She's serving the devil now, but imagine if she were born again, speaking in tongues, and talking about the fire in her music as a Christian artist.

00:14:17.959 --> 00:14:37.850
We have a lot of power on this YouTube channel with all of us praying together.

00:14:37.850 --> 00:14:46.251
Let's be an army for Jesus.

00:14:46.251 --> 00:14:51.160
I've talked enough; let's pray.

00:15:00.160 --> 00:15:00.516
You can take your communion; I'll pray alongside you.

00:15:09.380 --> 00:15:15.120
Father, we lift up the body before you and thank you for the communion.

00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:29.502
Your body was broken and beaten for us, and by your stripes we are healed.

00:15:32.227 --> 00:15:47.889
We lift it up and thank you, Father, that you were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities.

00:15:47.889 --> 00:16:00.680
We say no sickness or disease can come near us because it violates our covenant of health.

00:16:12.377 --> 00:17:46.235
Father, I thank you for the blood that covers us and eradicates our sin.

00:17:48.393 --> 00:18:37.953
We plead the blood of Jesus over us today from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

00:18:37.953 --> 00:23:52.464
Now, Lord, we lift up Elon Musk and I call him saved in the name of Jesus.

00:23:53.226 --> 00:24:41.151
I command the enemy to release his life and speak a radical visitation from you.

00:24:41.151 --> 00:25:02.999
Manifest yourself to him in a supernatural way.

00:25:09.510 --> 00:25:22.989
I thank you that Elon Musk's eyes are open and that the eyes of his understanding would be enlightened.

00:25:56.152 --> 00:26:01.915
I speak to his eyes right now that they are no longer blind.

00:26:22.800 --> 00:27:28.004
It doesn't matter what he thinks now; we call laborers across his path and a stirring in his spirit like a furnace.

00:27:35.431 --> 00:27:42.350
In the name of Jesus, he would be a voice for the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:27:42.350 --> 00:27:54.480
I'm going to pray in the spirit for him now.

00:29:52.240 --> 00:29:57.342
We call the breaking of darkness off of his life in the name of Jesus.

00:29:57.342 --> 00:30:02.244
We pray over his eyes.

00:30:02.244 --> 00:30:09.519
I see his heart, Lord.

00:30:11.600 --> 00:30:22.880
We thank you, Father, that he is radically born again today.

00:30:22.880 --> 00:30:34.259
Everyone wants to be loved and accepted.

00:30:34.259 --> 00:31:13.679
Holy Spirit, move on the man.

00:31:18.290 --> 00:31:26.627
We call the bondage and baggage of life to break off of him today.

00:31:26.627 --> 00:31:43.790
Any darkness or people influencing him, we call them to be removed in Jesus' name.

00:32:10.594 --> 00:32:11.011
I see a specific darkness regarding a woman; Satan, you've been found out.

00:32:11.011 --> 00:32:49.839
Thank you, Holy Spirit, for showing me more.

00:32:57.229 --> 00:33:15.980
We will pray for Elon Musk for the next 20 days.

00:33:25.119 --> 00:33:25.559
Now, Lord, we pray over this House.

00:33:30.345 --> 00:33:36.684
We call for a breakthrough in the House seats.

00:33:55.058 --> 00:33:58.799
We command the enemy to get his hand off the seats and bow his knee in the name of Jesus.

00:33:58.799 --> 00:34:02.249
We call it done.

00:34:02.249 --> 00:34:27.841
We thank you for the manifestation of what we're believing for concerning the House, not just barely scraping by, but having what we need.

00:34:31.079 --> 00:34:43.354
I call all corruption and hidden ballots to be revealed in the name of Jesus.

00:34:44.708 --> 00:34:55.564
I command the plots of the wicked to be exposed.

00:35:08.459 --> 00:35:08.839
We pray over the people Donald Trump is putting in his cabinet.

00:35:08.839 --> 00:35:22.000
I call for godly people around him, men and women with the mind of Christ.

00:35:23.650 --> 00:35:47.249
We call for supernatural wisdom over his mind for such a time as this to turn this nation around.

00:35:47.249 --> 00:36:02.253
I thank you, Lord, that he would be another King David who takes the head off the giant.

00:36:02.253 --> 00:36:13.119
I thank you for the finances to turn around.

00:36:20.750 --> 00:36:23.427
We want a revival no matter what it takes.

00:36:23.427 --> 00:36:41.276
We tell our flesh to shut up and we rise up higher with the fire.

00:36:41.276 --> 00:36:47.862
We are not moved by what we see or feel.

00:37:00.655 --> 00:37:00.910
We walk with the Spirit of the Lord today.

00:37:06.733 --> 00:37:07.247
The best is yet to come.

00:37:22.015 --> 00:37:22.570
We are the salt of the earth.

00:37:28.839 --> 00:37:39.590
I thank you that today is a day of great turnaround.

00:37:44.311 --> 00:38:02.600
I pray for every person who's bound by a demonic spirit in their home.

00:38:09.440 --> 00:38:13.196
I speak you free in the name of Jesus.

00:38:13.618 --> 00:38:24.326
Holy Spirit, move through this camera and into their rooms.

00:38:24.839 --> 00:38:32.979
You are free from that oppression right now.

00:38:34.384 --> 00:38:37.050
Don't be afraid; the devil is leaving.

00:38:37.050 --> 00:38:41.263
You are free indeed.

00:38:41.263 --> 00:38:48.600
I speak life over your mind and body.

00:39:03.417 --> 00:39:05.920
There is no more demonic hindrance.

00:39:05.920 --> 00:39:18.133
Some of you have multiple things manifesting; they are getting out of you now.

00:39:27.131 --> 00:39:36.742
You must get the Word of God inside your heart so they cannot come back.

00:39:36.742 --> 00:39:42.866
Keep your house full of the Word.

00:39:42.866 --> 00:39:52.600
Thank you, Jesus, for healing and deliverance.

00:39:54.200 --> 00:40:01.971
We walk in your goodness and peace.

00:40:01.971 --> 00:40:06.786
I'll do another video tomorrow.

00:40:09.818 --> 00:40:13.594
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:40:13.594 --> 00:40:19.780
No weapon formed against you shall prosper.

00:40:19.780 --> 00:40:24.125
These are our greatest hours.

00:40:24.125 --> 00:40:48.912
He chose you to be here for such a time as this because he knew you had what it takes to withstand the darkness and submit to Him.

00:41:02.297 --> 00:41:07.555
Have confidence because Jesus loves you.

00:41:11.864 --> 00:41:20.744
I want to hear Him say, "Well done, good and faithful servant.

00:41:35.620 --> 00:41:35.960
" We have work to do; occupy until He comes.

00:41:35.960 --> 00:41:57.880
If you are new here and want to learn more about the baptism of the Holy Spirit, find the book 'Why Tongues' by Brother Hagin.

00:41:57.880 --> 00:42:14.746
