00:42:14.746 --> 00:42:22.551
Subscribe if you'd like; the Lord told us we're going to have a million people praying here.

00:42:22.551 --> 00:42:30.029
Like the video and click the bell.

00:42:30.029 --> 00:42:36.680
Remember, Jesus is the Healer and He loves you.

00:42:36.680 --> 00:42:46.880
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:42:48.053 --> 00:42:55.509
God bless you all, and we will see you again tomorrow.

00:42:55.509 --> 00:42:56.777
Bye-bye.
